<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About | MindVault</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-brain gradient-text"></i> MindVault</h2>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about" style="color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">About</a>
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="form-section">
        <div class="form-card glass-panel" style="max-width: 600px; text-align: left;">
            <h1 style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 20px;">About <span class="gradient-text">MindVault</span></h1>

            <div style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px;">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    MindVault started as a simple backend engineering project, but has evolved into a vision for the
                    future of knowledge management.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    Our goal is to seamlessly integrate Artificial Intelligence into the note-taking process, allowing
                    users to not just store information, but to actively synthesize, understand, and generate new
                    insights from it.
                </p>

                <div
                    style="background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1); border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-cyan); padding: 15px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--text-primary);">
                    "The mind is not a vessel to be filled, but a fire to be kindled." - Plutarch
                </div>

                <p>
                    Currently, MindVault features a beautiful, state-of-the-art interface. The underlying AI mechanics
                    are constantly being researched and developed to bring you the best possible experience.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Create Your Vault <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"
                        style="margin-left: 8px;"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script src="/theme.js"></script>
</body>

</html>